[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1024","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1024.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1255","title":"Hyperseek 远程配置修改漏洞","description":"Hyperseek 是一款搜索引擎软件，其 admin.cgi 管理接口存在未授权访问漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可直接调用 admin.cgi 并传入 edit_file 参数，从而修改 Hyperseek 的配置文件，导致搜索结果劫持、恶意重定向或服务异常。该漏洞利用方式简单，危害中等，CVSS 评分 5.0。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1255"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:02.930","remediation":"Hyperseek 是一款已停止维护的软件（自 1999 年后无更新），admin.cgi 未做任何身份验证即可被远程调用。建议以下措施：①在 Web 服务器层（Apache .htaccess 或 Nginx 配置）为 /cgi-bin/admin.cgi 路径添加 HTTP 基本认证，限制仅授权用户可访问；②在防火墙上限制源 IP，仅允许管理网段访问该脚本路径；③由于厂商已停止维护，建议迁移至活跃维护的替代搜索方案（如 Apache Solr 或 Elasticsearch）以消除长期风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.rootshell.com/archive-j457nxiqi3gq59dv/199902/hyperseek.txt.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1914","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1255.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1255","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1255.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1255.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5hp3-5xjh-3v56/GHSA-5hp3-5xjh-3v56.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87851/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1255.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e2ff807e9fd18d30d388cc2c559c111ff993a143/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1024.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1023","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1023.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1254","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/98/NT 4.0 ICMP重定向消息拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95/98/NT 4.0 操作系统内核网络协议栈在处理 ICMP（Internet Control Message Protocol）重定向消息时存在设计缺陷，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过伪造路由器发送的 ICMP 重定向报文，欺骗目标系统修改其路由表条目，将网络流量重定向至恶意路径，导致目标主机网络连接中断，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 95/98/NT 4.0 等早期版本，攻击者无需任何认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1254"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:02.813","remediation":"Windows 95/98/NT 4.0 均已终止支持且不再有安全更新，建议升级至 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2016+ 等受支持版本。如在旧系统上需临时缓解，可将注册表 `HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\Tcpip\\Parameters\\EnableICMPRedirect` 设为 `0` 以禁用 ICMP 重定向处理。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92099515709467&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1947","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1254.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1254","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1254.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1254.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-72gc-hjc8-g27